00:04:35.290 --> 00:04:38.072
neyen un shnaydn un moln.

00:04:38.415 --> 00:04:42.142
un dernokh hob ikh khasene gehat, in akhtsetn, ⟨⟩,

00:04:42.364 --> 00:04:43.921
tsu akhtsn yor.

00:04:44.052 --> 00:04:45.854
 far di khasene,

00:04:45.854 --> 00:04:49.564
