fun dayn onkl, kenstu mir dertseyln a bisl?

00:04:51.966 --> 00:04:56.313
d- der onkl, der onkl iz gevorn zeyer orem dernokh,

00:04:57.231 --> 00:04:59.908
un mayn tante iz geshtorbn,

00:05:00.420 --> 00:05:03.519
