di mame hot gearbet sh-, gehaltn a,

00:05:10.972 --> 00:05:13.138
a varshtat fun shnayderay,

00:05:13.161 --> 00:05:17.272
ober zi hot mir gedarft oyshaltn un altsding aleyn makhn.

00:05:18.055 --> 00:05:20.276
un du host ir geholfn?

00:05:20.080 --> 00:05:22.554
ikh hob, dernokh hob ikh geholfn, ye.

00:05:22.628 --> 00:05:25.499
ven iz, ⟨⟩, ven iz der,

00:05:25.499 --> 00:05:27.651
der UNCLE gevorn orem?

00:05:27.910 --> 00:05:30.384
ven iz d- ikh veys ven der onkl...

00:05:29.547 --> 00:05:32.117
nu, vi alt bistu gevezn ven bist

00:05:32.117 --> 00:05:33.911
tsurikgeganen aheym?

00:05:33.816 --> 00:05:36.324
beshas ikh fleg zayn bayn onkl?

00:05:36.043 --> 00:05:39.884
ven bist shoyn geganen tsurik aheym tsu dayn mame.

00:05:39.148 --> 00:05:42.978
 nu, bin ikh geven mistome tsen yor, tsvelf,

00:05:42.760 --> 00:05:45.707
 biz tsen, tsvelf, bist...

00:05:43.013 --> 00:05:44.542
draytsn yor.

00:05:44.582 --> 00:05:46.444
vayl ikh hob zikh gelernt in,

00:05:46.444 --> 00:05:48.812
in yidishe, alts in yidish.

00:05:48.953 --> 00:05:52.761
afile in a kinder-gortn bin ikh oykh geven yidish.

00:05:49.035 --> 00:05:49.821
UNK

00:05:53.188 --> 00:05:55.949
host nisht gegat shvestern un bridern?

00:05:55.213 --> 00:05:58.828
neyn, vayle mayn tate iz geharget gevorn.

00:05:59.466 --> 00:06:00.455
yung.

00:05:59.483 --> 00:06:01.890
⟨un⟩ ikh bin geborn gevorn.

00:06:01.727 --> 00:06:02.885
zeyer yung.

00:06:02.925 --> 00:06:04.573
hob ikh nit gehat.

00:06:04.714 --> 00:06:07.364
un dayn mame hot nisht khasene gegat?

00:06:07.093 --> 00:06:09.162
neyn, tsulib mir.

00:06:10.452 --> 00:06:11.728
tsulib dir?

00:06:11.194 --> 00:06:12.278
ye.

00:06:13.573 --> 00:06:16.378
un, du gedenkst,

00:06:16.378 --> 00:06:19.964
KHAVERIM host gegat, andere kinder?

