 KHAVERIM, dayne KHAVERIM, mit vemen host, ⟨,⟩ geshpilt?

00:06:21.927 --> 00:06:23.659
mayne kh-...

00:06:24.471 --> 00:06:27.534
ye. nu, ⟨i-⟩ avade gedenk ikh. ikh ho-...

00:06:26.280 --> 00:06:27.691
mit vemenen?

00:06:27.534 --> 00:06:30.847
ikh hob gehat khavertes vos ikh hob zikh gelernt mit zey.

00:06:30.853 --> 00:06:34.694
mir hobn tsuzamen gezungen in dem grestn Vilbig khor,

00:06:35.157 --> 00:06:36.163
ya?

00:06:35.342 --> 00:06:37.389
a yidisher Vilbig khor.

00:06:37.350 --> 00:06:38.508
yidishe...

00:06:37.389 --> 00:06:40.061
zeyer a sheyne gezelshaft.

00:06:40.506 --> 00:06:43.369
vi alt, vi alt bistu geven ⟨den⟩?

00:06:40.573 --> 00:06:42.414
ober ⟨may-⟩... ha?

00:06:42.714 --> 00:06:48.397
ikh bin geven zekhtsn p⟨UNK⟩ tsu akhtsn hob ikh bakant, mayn man hob ikh bakant frier.

00:06:48.799 --> 00:06:52.396
er iz gekumen, er iz elter geven far mir oyf tsen yor,

00:06:52.825 --> 00:06:56.835
un er iz gekumen tsu undz in shtub un er iz gevezn,

00:06:57.094 --> 00:07:00.429
er iz geven a guter spetsyalist, a fakh-man.

00:07:01.127 --> 00:07:05.491
un, ikh bin im gefeln gevorn. ikh bin geven a oreme,

00:07:05.785 --> 00:07:09.120
un er hot mit mir... ikh bin geven a sheyne zeyer a mol...

00:07:09.227 --> 00:07:11.707
un er hot mit mir khasene gehat.

00:07:12.568 --> 00:07:16.831
UNK far di khasene, in velekhe yor iz, hostu im bakent?

00:07:16.939 --> 00:07:19.413
 in velkhn yor hob ikh im bakent?

00:07:19.572 --> 00:07:23.160
ikh hob im bakent mit, ikh hob khasene gehat in,

00:07:23.487 --> 00:07:25.877
in akht un draysik, dakht zikh,

00:07:26.052 --> 00:07:31.800
⟨ober⟩ ikh hob im bakent a por yor frier, a dray yor. er fleg kumen tsu mayne a kuzine.

00:07:32.481 --> 00:07:33.842
baym UNCLE?

00:07:33.385 --> 00:07:36.119
b- b- neyn, bay mir in shtub.

00:07:36.497 --> 00:07:42.003
iz geven, di mame hot gelernt, shnayderay a kuzinke vos zi hot gelebt in a

00:07:42.003 --> 00:07:43.528
kleyne shtetl.

00:07:43.602 --> 00:07:45.857
a, an andere kuzinke. host ge-...

00:07:44.665 --> 00:07:51.121
ya. flegt er kumen. zi iz geven a eltere, ober ikh bin geven nokh a yunge; kh'hob zikh gelernt in klas.

00:07:51.516 --> 00:07:53.906
ober ikh bin im geven gefeln,

00:07:54.334 --> 00:07:57.528
un, dernokh hobn mir khasene gehat.

00:07:57.135 --> 00:08:02.157
host nokh gegat, nokh, nokh UNCLEs mit, tantes?

00:08:01.949 --> 00:08:02.949
vos?

00:08:02.400 --> 00:08:06.157
host gegat nokh mishpokhe, nokh, UNCLEs?

00:08:04.746 --> 00:08:08.722
mishpokhe, onkls mit tantes, fun mayn tatn.

00:08:08.695 --> 00:08:10.471
in, in di zelbe shtot?

00:08:10.062 --> 00:08:12.570
fun, di zelbe Vilne.

00:08:12.576 --> 00:08:14.713
ir hot zikh getrofn mit zey?

00:08:14.280 --> 00:08:18.104
ikh fleg... vi den? ikh fleg kumen tsu mayne kuzangen.

00:08:18.347 --> 00:08:20.484
eyner iz geharget gevorn,

00:08:20.676 --> 00:08:24.197
 in, ⟨, g-⟩ vi s'iz gevorn nayn un draysik di krig.

00:08:24.456 --> 00:08:26.222
a sheyner BAKHUR.

00:08:27.797 --> 00:08:30.592
i- ir vet mir shpeter dertseyln fun,

00:08:30.592 --> 00:08:34.435
fun di krig-tsayt; ikh vil nokh fregn far di krig-tsayt.

00:08:34.058 --> 00:08:34.963
ya.

00:08:34.435 --> 00:08:38.199
 day- in dayn, in UNCLE's, shtub,

00:08:38.199 --> 00:08:42.725
hot men gemakht, di yontoyvim fun, yidishe yontoyvim?

00:08:42.057 --> 00:08:46.860
mayn mame iz geven mit mir. mir flegn shtendik forn tsu gast tsu ⟨i-⟩...

00:08:46.967 --> 00:08:51.365
