00:08:51.372 --> 00:08:52.513
gornisht?

00:08:52.063 --> 00:08:53.170
neyn.

00:08:52.688 --> 00:08:55.213
vu zent ir geforn oyf yontoyvim?

00:08:55.405 --> 00:09:00.242
oyf yontoyvim, tsu mayne, tsu ir mishpokhe. zi hot gehat shvesterkinder.

00:09:00.028 --> 00:09:01.794
oykh in Vilne?

00:09:00.889 --> 00:09:02.621
alts in Vilne.

00:09:02.796 --> 00:09:05.321
un vos gedenkstu fun di yontoyvim?

00:09:05.698 --> 00:09:11.463
ikh gedenk UNK mir flegn kumen oyf a yontev, di mame flegt mir firn far a hentele.

00:09:11.875 --> 00:09:15.767
⟨un⟩ dernokh, az ikh bin shoyn gevorn greser, hob ikh gehat khavertes.

00:09:15.975 --> 00:09:19.917
kh'hob gehat a sheyne gezelshaft vayl ikh hob gezungen in khor.

00:09:20.110 --> 00:09:23.040
kh'hob zikh gelernt in a yidishe gimnazye.

00:09:23.198 --> 00:09:27.157
ober, gelebt hob ikh zeyer in a poshete gas:

00:09:27.248 --> 00:09:29.705
in Vilne oyf Yidishe gas.

00:09:30.707 --> 00:09:33.232
der nomen fun di gas iz gevezn...?

00:09:32.142 --> 00:09:34.299
Yidishe gas.

00:09:33.728 --> 00:09:37.586
ale mentshn dort zenen gevezn yidn?

00:09:35.749 --> 00:09:39.374
vos hobn gevoynt, ya. ikh hob dernokh a khaverte,

00:09:39.853 --> 00:09:44.352
vos zi lebt itster oykh, vos ikh fleg keseyder kumen tsu zey in shtub.

00:09:44.646 --> 00:09:47.778
mit ire an eltere shvester hob ikh zikh gekhavert.

00:09:48.342 --> 00:09:51.694
 ⟨m'iz, s'iz⟩ mir, kh'hob a bild,

00:09:52.678 --> 00:09:56.401
hobn zey gefunen, vos ikh hob gezungen in Vilbig khor,

00:09:56.577 --> 00:09:59.409
un mir zaynen geven oyf a kontsert in

00:09:59.409 --> 00:10:03.084
Oshmene. dos iz lebn dortn. hob ikh aza bild

00:10:03.158 --> 00:10:05.801
fun ale khaveyrim mit khavertes.

00:10:05.571 --> 00:10:08.147
hostu di bild bay dir in shtub?

00:10:06.735 --> 00:10:07.522
ya.

00:10:07.924 --> 00:10:08.924
ya.

00:10:08.322 --> 00:10:11.921
du vest undz shpeter vayzn dize bild, bild.

00:10:09.705 --> 00:10:11.876
ya, ya, ya, ya.

