mit di khave-... dos iz eyn un eyntsike bild vos s'iz geblibn?

00:10:15.274 --> 00:10:17.192
ikh bin geven eyne.

00:10:17.586 --> 00:10:22.727
un, ir gedenkt, ir zent gevezn a freylekh meydele?

00:10:19.695 --> 00:10:20.999
 mayn man?

00:10:22.429 --> 00:10:23.604
zeyer.

00:10:24.184 --> 00:10:27.671
zeyer: shtendik tantsn un farbrengen,

00:10:28.032 --> 00:10:31.589
un mir flegn geyn oyf tents, un mir flegn geyn umetum.

00:10:31.457 --> 00:10:35.349
mit, mit, KHA- KHAVEROT, mit KHAVERIM?

00:10:32.807 --> 00:10:36.328
 mit KHAVERIM, un, un, ya, ober dernokh

00:10:36.351 --> 00:10:39.078
⟨hot zi-⟩ kh'hob gehat frier oykhet a khaver,

00:10:39.237 --> 00:10:42.490
un mayn mame hot mir mit im nit gelozn khasene hobn,

00:10:42.490 --> 00:10:44.749
vayl er iz geven a kleyner fardiner.

00:10:45.447 --> 00:10:47.314
er hot nisht fardint gut?

00:10:46.358 --> 00:10:50.351
er hot nit fardint gut. ikh bin a tsayt mit im gegangen.

00:10:50.728 --> 00:10:53.827
ober der hot, der hot fardint, un er hot glaykh

00:10:53.952 --> 00:10:59.346
gedungen a dire un mir zaynen arayn, un ikh hob di gantse tsayt geholfn im arbetn.

00:10:59.554 --> 00:11:04.998
kenst dertseyln undz, fun dayn khasene: vi azoy iz geven, ver hot gemakht di khasene?

00:11:04.049 --> 00:11:07.185
di khas- di kh- di khasene, mir hobn gemakht,

00:11:07.185 --> 00:11:11.478
bay undz flegt men makhn a, ⟨a⟩ khupe bayn kazyonem rabiner.

00:11:12.750 --> 00:11:15.164
s'iz geven a rabiner,

00:11:14.505 --> 00:11:15.326
ya.

00:11:16.530 --> 00:11:19.325
UNK dortn gemakht mayn khupe,

00:11:19.652 --> 00:11:23.678
un s'iz geven a MESIBA bay mayn onkl in shtub nokh.

00:11:24.512 --> 00:11:29.878
f-, vifl, ⟨,⟩ vi fil mentshn zenen gevezn? ver iz gevezn UNK...?

00:11:24.774 --> 00:11:26.342
⟨baym⟩...

00:11:28.393 --> 00:11:32.082
s'iz geven a sakh: di kh- di, di mishpokhe un,

00:11:32.325 --> 00:11:35.255
un kh'hob gehat khavertes, khaveyrim.

00:11:33.574 --> 00:11:37.242
vifl mentshn geven? kenst dertseyln fun di khasene?

00:11:35.920 --> 00:11:38.934
oyf di KHATUNA, di, in shtub,

00:11:38.957 --> 00:11:43.649
geven mistome draysik, fertsik mentshn. ikh ken gedenk⟨en? shoyn a...⟩

