00:11:45.255 --> 00:11:46.785
s'iz geven, ya.

00:11:47.057 --> 00:11:50.139
in, akht un draysikstn yor?

00:11:49.808 --> 00:11:50.747
ya.

00:11:50.348 --> 00:11:51.169
ya?

00:11:51.799 --> 00:11:56.248
un, ir gedenkt, voser kleyd ⟨ir zent⟩ gevezn?

00:11:55.377 --> 00:11:57.092
s'iz vos far a kleyd?

00:11:56.642 --> 00:11:57.581
ya?

00:11:57.435 --> 00:12:01.259
mayn khaverte iz, ikh ho- ikh bin geven nit keyn farmeglekhe,

00:12:01.587 --> 00:12:05.243
nor mayn khaverte, fun Amerike flegt men shikn,

00:12:05.738 --> 00:12:09.748
a onkl flegt ir shikn. hob ikh oysgeklibn bay ir a kleyd,

00:12:09.923 --> 00:12:11.722
a tsigl-farb kleyd,

00:12:12.032 --> 00:12:13.663
un ikh bin gekumen

00:12:12.437 --> 00:12:14.523
vos⟨er f-⟩ kolir di kleyd?

00:12:13.720 --> 00:12:15.097
aza...

00:12:15.120 --> 00:12:18.911
un ikh bin avek tsu der khupe, nor az ikh bin geshtanen unter der khupe...

00:12:19.339 --> 00:12:22.235
frier iz mayn man's mishpokhe,

00:12:22.815 --> 00:12:25.883
 mayn man's mishpokhe iz geven. zey hobn mir eyn mol,

00:12:25.883 --> 00:12:29.171
hobn zey gefregt, "meydele, ven vet kumen di kale?"

00:12:29.262 --> 00:12:31.787
vayl ikh hob oysgezen zeyer yung.

00:12:33.379 --> 00:12:35.550
un ikh bin geven a sheyne a mol.

00:12:33.447 --> 00:12:34.592
UNK

00:12:35.303 --> 00:12:38.081
⟨,⟩ voser kolir iz gevezn di kleydl?

00:12:37.412 --> 00:12:40.764
di kleyd iz geven a, a tsigl-farb.

00:12:40.888 --> 00:12:43.721
dos iz geven, ikh gedenk vi haynt.

00:12:43.133 --> 00:12:44.342
nisht vays.

00:12:43.721 --> 00:12:45.320
ober,

00:12:45.681 --> 00:12:49.061
dernokh bin ikh geshtanen in a zhaket mit, m-

00:12:49.061 --> 00:12:53.454
mit a vayse beret, mit lange ⟨shiler-lokn⟩. ikh bin geven zeyer

00:12:54.321 --> 00:12:57.085
sheyn. dernokh hob ikh geholfn mayn man, un,

00:12:57.085 --> 00:13:00.171
un nokh di khasene hobn mir oykh gelebt oyf Yidishe gas.

00:13:00.362 --> 00:13:03.984
dortn hobn mir gedungen a dire, iz eyn tsimer iz geven

00:13:04.041 --> 00:13:05.908
di maysterskaye,

00:13:06.066 --> 00:13:10.059
heyst dos der arbet, un in tsveytn tsimer hobn mir gelebt.

00:13:10.335 --> 00:13:13.653
dos iz geven bizn nayn un draysikstn yor.

00:13:13.407 --> 00:13:16.134
vos hot ayer, man geton?

00:13:16.039 --> 00:13:20.507
 er iz geven a spetsyalist fun makhn modeln oyf shikh,

00:13:20.258 --> 00:13:21.112
aha.

00:13:20.507 --> 00:13:21.905
a modelyor.

00:13:22.317 --> 00:13:25.433
er flegt tseykhenen zhurnaln far Moskve

00:13:25.472 --> 00:13:26.850
un umetum.

00:13:27.632 --> 00:13:30.049
un du host im geholfn?

00:13:28.628 --> 00:13:32.469
in nayn un draysikstn yor iz gevorn di milkhome.

00:13:32.779 --> 00:13:35.172
un ikh bin nokh geven mit mayn mamen

00:13:35.172 --> 00:13:36.975
oyf a zumer-voynung.

00:13:37.909 --> 00:13:41.356
un mayn man iz gekumen oyf gikh ⟨un hot⟩ undz opgenumen.

00:13:41.356 --> 00:13:43.994
dos iz geven, avgust iz geven di krig.

00:13:44.355 --> 00:13:46.036
dan hostu geher-...

00:13:44.406 --> 00:13:48.045
nayn un draysik⟨t-⟩ iz gevorn di krig mit di daytshn.

00:13:48.017 --> 00:13:50.072
du host gehert fun di krig

00:13:50.072 --> 00:13:51.465
dos ershte mol,

00:13:50.093 --> 00:13:51.572
UNK ⟨dos⟩ ikh hob ge-...

00:13:51.465 --> 00:13:58.018
dos ershte mol ven dayn man iz gekumen tsu zu- tsu, tsu aykh nemen dikh tsurik aheym?

00:13:55.156 --> 00:13:59.688
y-, ya, s'iz gevorn plutslung, di daytshn zaynen...

00:13:58.834 --> 00:13:59.773
ya?

00:13:59.982 --> 00:14:03.705
un dayn man iz gekumen un gezogt, "s'iz do a krig."

00:14:02.901 --> 00:14:08.683
gekumen aheym tsurik zaynen mir; mir zaynen geven oyf a zumer-voynung, ikh mit mayn mamen mit a,

00:14:08.706 --> 00:14:10.134
mit di meydele.

00:14:10.596 --> 00:14:12.142
velekhe meydele?

00:14:11.305 --> 00:14:14.913
ikh hob dokh gehat a meydele, vos in geto, ⟨⟩...

00:14:13.380 --> 00:14:16.867
du host shoyn geha- -hat a mey-... vi alt iz zi geven?

00:14:14.913 --> 00:14:16.850
ya.

00:14:17.143 --> 00:14:20.064
in geto iz zi geven UNK...

00:14:18.983 --> 00:14:20.764
nokh far di geto?

00:14:20.756 --> 00:14:23.448
far di geto iz zi geven a kl-...

00:14:20.764 --> 00:14:22.791
ve- ven di, di,

00:14:23.421 --> 00:14:25.339
ven di krig iz aroys?

